video.title: VFestival Perth Australia part 3
video.description: Amid the merry Perth throng at the Australia VFestival, what was Bob from music.virgin.com's priority? More backstage interviews with headline acts such as Duran Duran, Smashing Pumpkins, The Presets and Queens Of The Stone Age? Nah - chips, chips and more chips. It's hungry work this festival reporting you know...
